Package com.esri.gpt.catalog.arcgis.metadata

Processing of service and dataset metadata associated with a referenced ArcGIS Server.

          Description

Interface Summary
IServiceInfoProvider Service info provider
 

Class Summary
AGSInterrogator Interrogates an ArcGIS server target to determine the REST and SOAP endpoints for an ArcGIS server services catalog.
AGSProcessor Processes resources associated with an ArcGIS server.
AGSProcessorConfig AGSProcessor configuration.
AGSSynchronizer Background thread to synchronize ArcGIS Server content with the metadata catalog.
AGSTarget Holds properties associated with an ArcGIS Server and the type of resource targetted for processing.
FeatureServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS globe service (GlobeServer).
GeocodeServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS locator service (GeocodeServer).
GeoDataServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS geodatabase service (GeoDataServer).
GeometryServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS geometry service (GeometryServer).
GlobeServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS globe service (GlobeServer).
GPServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS geoprocessing service (GPServer).
ImageServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS image service (ImageServer).
MapServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS map service (MapServer).
MobileServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS mobile service (MobileServer).
NAServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS network analysis service (NAServer).
OGCServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS server service implementing an OGC type (WMS, WFS, WCS).
SearchServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS globe service (GlobeServer).
ServiceHandler Super-class associated with the collection and publication of metadata for an ArcGIS Server service.
ServiceHandlerFactory A factory for instantiating handlers capabable of processing specific ArcGIS Server service types.
ServiceInfo Stores basic properties about a service.
ServiceInfo.LayerInfo  
ServiceInfoProvider Service info provider.
ServiceInfoProviderAdapter  
WCSServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS WCS service (WCSServer).
WFSServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS WFS service (WFSServer).
WMSServerHandler Handles the collection of metadata for an ArcGIS WMS service (WMSServer).
